            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1349212923,
            "creation_date": 1349212923,
            "body": "<p>When you want to execute the program, you specifiy the <em>class<\/em> name rather than the file name:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>java HelloWorld\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Don't use <code>java HelloWorld.java<\/code>, for instance.<\/p>\n",
